  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet adorable animal friends in the physics-based puzzle game Animal Shake.</h2></strong><br><br>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/5449e58d59cdff7e41a5edb1b7640834.poster.avif?t=1731609006\" width=346 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/5449e58d59cdff7e41a5edb1b7640834.webm?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/5449e58d59cdff7e41a5edb1b7640834.mp4?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　When animals of the same kind meet, they become a higher-level animal.<br><br>　<br>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/50b13efa0a29b594845aeb781221f093.poster.avif?t=1731609006\" width=346 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/50b13efa0a29b594845aeb781221f093.webm?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/50b13efa0a29b594845aeb781221f093.mp4?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　From small squirrels to cats, tigers, bears, and elephants, there are various sizes of animal friends.<br>　Space inside the box is limited. Make good use of the space.<br><br>　<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Made a mistake? Shake Time!</h2></strong><br><br>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/65b7319f1a0bd3c744eefcadd823f6bd.poster.avif?t=1731609006\" width=346 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/65b7319f1a0bd3c744eefcadd823f6bd.webm?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/65b7319f1a0bd3c744eefcadd823f6bd.mp4?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　Tilt or shake the box to solve the game.<br><br>　<br>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/01aea286dcc838cda2ca3c4a7c15da38.poster.avif?t=1731609006\" width=346 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/01aea286dcc838cda2ca3c4a7c15da38.webm?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/01aea286dcc838cda2ca3c4a7c15da38.mp4?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　Be careful! If you shake too hard, animal friends may come out of the box.<br><br>　<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Carefully, Quickly.</h2></strong><br><br>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/66629901c6d761bb7b0b98c8967a7bf2.poster.avif?t=1731609006\" width=346 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/66629901c6d761bb7b0b98c8967a7bf2.webm?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/66629901c6d761bb7b0b98c8967a7bf2.mp4?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　In Land Mode, which requires caution, the Shake Gauge needed when shaking the box is filled when animals are merged.<br><br>　<br>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/7e9735a3cff24a2ca039485bde07c4cb.poster.avif?t=1731609006\" width=346 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/7e9735a3cff24a2ca039485bde07c4cb.webm?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/7e9735a3cff24a2ca039485bde07c4cb.mp4?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　Want a speedy play? In Sky Mode, you can quickly pour out the animals and shake the box without any restrictions<br><br>　<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chipmunk as heavy as an Elephant?</h2></strong><br><br>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/bae0d037b851b31d696e7faff7938a2f.poster.avif?t=1731609006\" width=346 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/bae0d037b851b31d696e7faff7938a2f.webm?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/bae0d037b851b31d696e7faff7938a2f.mp4?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　Light gravity like the moon, animals trapped in triangular ice, bouncy and elastic mode, etc.<br>　You can combine mutations that change or add rules to the game for a variety of gaming experiences.<br><br>　<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The end is a new beginning.</h2></strong><br><br>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/c0234f1f861251be8ea97b6ff433b259.poster.avif?t=1731609006\" width=346 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/c0234f1f861251be8ea97b6ff433b259.webm?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869960/extras/c0234f1f861251be8ea97b6ff433b259.mp4?t=1731609006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>　What happens when the biggest animals meet? As you become skilled in the game, new challenges await.",
